This paper is about cyber intrusion detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper proposes a new method using generative adversarial networks (GANs), which involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions using image processing techniques to preprocess the data, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV).
